[div class=p 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/Noxxa 
		"Noxxa
	]a
	": I don't feel that this movie does enough to really call itself a full game completion (as conforming to 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=Vault|href=/LegacyPages/Vault)
	" rules). This movie does not reach any meaningful end screen - after completing, it goes straight back to the Vs. Com settings menu. This is unlike the actual single-player modes, which do provide such end screens (be they as simple as a "you are a Tetris master!" screen). The fact that this movie picks the easiest settings to defeat the AI with also does not feel right.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"As the movie does not reach an acceptable end screen or other means that can really be defined as clearing the game, I am rejecting this submission.
]div
